name: Canis rufus
description:
Every year during the third full week of October it's Wolf Awareness Week. To celebrate we're introducing you to the wolf species and subspecies found throughout North America.

Common Name: Red Wolf
Latin Name: Canis rufus
Location: North Carolina

Red wolves are a critically endangered species, with a total wild population estimated at around 20 to 25 individuals.
